•—ВҪ SQL</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div className=\"stat-card\">\r\n                        <p className=\"label\">TГҹв•—ГІng в”ҖГҰГЈГӯn hв”ңГЎng</p>\r\n                        <h2 style={{fontSize: '2rem'}}>{finance.transactions.length}</h2>\r\n                        <p style={{color: '#64748b', fontSize: '0.85rem'}}>LГҹв•‘Г‘y tГҹв•—ВҪ bГҹв•‘Гәng OrderItem</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div style={{display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: '2fr 1fr', gap: '30px', marginTop: '30px'}}>\r\n                    <div className=\"content-card\">\r\n                        <h3>LГҹв•—ГҜch sГҹв•—ВЎ giao dГҹв•—ГҜch gГҹв•‘Вәn в”ҖГҰв”ңГіy</h3>\r\n                        <table className=\"course-table\" style={{marginTop: '20px'}}>\r\n                            <thead>\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <th>Mв”ңГә GD</th>\r\n                                    <th>Khв”ңв”Ӯa hГҹв•—Г¬c</th>\r\n                                    <th>SГҹв•—ГҰ tiГҹв•—Гјn</th>\r\n                                    <th>TrГҹв•‘Гӯng thв”ңГӯi</th>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </thead>\r\n                            <tbody>\r\n                                {finance.transactions.length === 0 ? <tr><td colSpan=\"4\">ChГЈв–‘a cв”ңв”Ӯ giao dГҹв•—ГҜch nв”ңГЎo.</td></tr> : finance.transactions.map(t => (\r\n                                    <tr key={t.id}>\r\n                                        <td style={{fontWeight: 600}}>{t.id}</td>\r\n                                        <td>{t.course}</td>\r\n                                        <td>{t.amount.toLocaleString()}Г”Г©ВҪ</td>\r\n                                        <td>\r\n                                            <span style={{\r\n                                                padding: '4px 10px', \r\n                                                borderRadius: '20px', \r\n                                                fontSize: '0.75rem',\r\n                                                background: t.status === 'Thв”ңГЎnh cв”ңв”Өng' ? '#f0fdf4' : '#fff7ed',\r\n                                                color: t.status === 'Thв”ңГЎnh cв”ңв”Өng' ? '#166534' : '#9a3412'\r\n                                            }}>\r\n                                                {t.status}\r\n                                            </span>\r\n                                        </td>\r\n                                    </tr>\r\n                                ))}\r\n                            </tbody>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div className=\"content-card\">\r\n                        <h3>Tв”ңГЎi khoГҹв•‘Гәn ngв”ңГіn hв”ңГЎng</h3>\r\n                        <div style={{marginTop: '20px', padding: '15px', border: '1px solid #e2e8f0', borderRadius: '8px', background: '#f8fafc'}}>\r\n                            <div style={{fontSize: '0.8rem', color: '#64748b'}}>Tв”ңВ¬n ngв”ңГіn hв”ңГЎng</div>\r\n                            <div style={{fontWeight: 600, marginBottom: '10px'}}>{finance.bank_info.bank_name}</div>\r\n                            <div style={{fontSize: '0.8rem', color: '#64748b'}}>SГҹв•—ГҰ tв”ңГЎi khoГҹв•‘Гәn</div>\r\n                            <div style={{fontWeight: 600, marginBottom: '10px'}}>{finance.bank_info.account_number}</div>\r\n                            <div style={{fontSize: '0.8rem', color: '#64748b'}}>ChГҹв•—Вә tв”ңГЎi khoГҹв•‘Гәn</div>\r\n                            <div style={{fontWeight: 600}}>{finance.bank_info.account_holder}</div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <button style={{width: '100%', marginTop: '20px', padding: '10px', background: 'none', border: '1px solid #0056d2', color: '#0056d2', borderRadius: '6px', cursor: 'pointer'}}>Thay в”ҖГҰГҹв•—ГІi thв”ңв”Өng tin</button>\r\n               